import React from 'react'
import { Switch, Route, BrowserRouter } from 'react-router-dom'
import Start from './pages/Start'
import './App.scss'


function App() {

    return (
        <BrowserRouter>
                <Switch>
                    <Route path='/' component={Start}/>
                </Switch>
        </BrowserRouter>
    )
}

export default App
